data.description: Welcome to 2901 Saint James Lane, a stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home situated on a cozy lot in the heart of Melbourne. This well-maintained gem is perfect for families and retirees alike, offering modern amenities & convenient access to nearby attractions. Step inside and marvel at the open kitchen, complete with stainless-steel appliances, an oversized island with ample storage, a built-in wine cooler, 42' cabinets, and elegant granite countertops. The contemporary ceramic tile flooring adds an extra touch of sophistication to this space.  Low HOA fee of just $225/year. Just a short distance away, you'll find the beautiful Wickham Park, boasting numerous recreational activities, such as swimming lakes, disc golf, volleyball, soccer, and more.  Don't miss your chance to own this incredible property located at James Landing. Make it your new home today and start creating cherished memories for years to come.
